About

Stephen Caffrey is a 64 year old American Actor. Born Stephen Edwin Caffrey on 27th September, 1959 in Cleveland, Ohio, USA, he is famous for Tour of Duty. His zodiac sign is Libra.

Tia Carrere is a 57 year old American Actress. Born Althea Rae Duhinio Janairo on 2nd January, 1967 in Honolulu, Hawaii, USA, she is famous for her roles as Jade Soong in the long-running ABC daytime soap opera General Hospital, Cassandra Wong in the 1992 comedy film Wayne's World and its 1993 sequel Wayne's World 2, Juno Skinner in the 1994 spy action comedy film True Lies, Nani Pelekai (voice) in the Lilo & Stitch franchise, Queen Tyr'ahnee (voice) in the Cartoon Network/Kids' WB/Boomerang animated comic science fiction series Duck Dodgers, Sydney Fox in the first-run syndicated action-adventure series Relic Hunter, Cha Cha in the HBO original sitcom Curb Your Enthusiasm, and Lady Danger in the Netflix original comedy-drama web series AJ and the Queen in a career that spans 1993-present and 1993–present and 1992–present and 1985-present and 1984–present and 1992–present. Her zodiac sign is Capricorn.
